Step-by-step instal ESS di Centos6

1. Clone Linov ESS with this git https://github.com/linovsoftware/LinovESS.git
2. composer install
3. bower install --allow-root
4. php -r "copy('.env.example', '.env');"
5. edit file .env
   APP_URL = <sesuai dengan nama situs>
   DB_CONNECTION=pgsql
   DB_HOST=127.0.0.1
   DB_PORT=3306
   DB_DATABASE=homestead
   DB_USERNAME=homestead
   DB_PASSWORD=secret
6. php artisan migrate



